    DEG_F_SEC_PER_BTU_IT = URIRef("http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/DEG_F-SEC-PER-BTU_IT")  #    The unit $\textit{Degree Fahrenheit Second per British thermal unit (international table)}$ is a non SI-conform unit    of the thermal resistance according to the Imperial system of units.   
